links.title: $WWD Woodward Schedules Fiscal 2020 Fourth Quarter and Full Year Earnings Release and Conference Call
links.description: FORT COLLINS, Colo., Nov. 05, 2020 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Woodward, Inc. (NASDAQ: WWD) announced today that it plans to report its fiscal 2020 fourth quarter and full year financial results at approximately 4:00 p.m. EST on Thursday, November 19, 2020. A news release will be issued at that time and a conference call will be held at 4:30 p.m.

links.title: Woodward, Inc.Common Stock Plans Quarterly Dividend of $0.08 (NASDAQ:WWD)
links.description: Woodward, Inc.Common Stock (NASDAQ:WWD) declared a quarterly dividend on Wednesday, September 23rd. Stockholders of record on Monday, November 16th will be given a dividend of 0.081 per share by the technology company on Monday, November 30th. This represents a $0.32 dividend on an annualized basis and a dividend yield of 0.43%.
